{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":594,"text":"I don't know why, but I'm continually amazed to think"},{"time":3819,"text":"that two and a half billion of us around the world"},{"time":6417,"text":"are connected to each other through the Internet"},{"time":8833,"text":"and that at any point in time"},{"time":10958,"text":"more than 30 percent of the world's population"},{"time":13708,"text":"can go online to learn, to create and to share."},{"time":18823,"text":"And the amount of time each of us is spending doing all of this"},{"time":22386,"text":"is also continuing to go grow."},{"time":24167,"text":"A recent study showed"},{"time":25625,"text":"that the young generation alone"},{"time":27125,"text":"is spending over eight hours a day online."},{"time":30396,"text":"As the parent of a nine-year-old girl,"},{"time":32562,"text":"that number seems awfully low."},{"time":34775,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36125,"text":"But just as the Internet has opened up the world for each and every one of us,"},{"time":40198,"text":"it has also opened up each and every one of us to the world."},{"time":43873,"text":"And increasingly, the price we're being asked to pay"},{"time":46729,"text":"for all of this connectedness"},{"time":47980,"text":"is our privacy."},{"time":49994,"text":"Today, what many of us would love to believe"},{"time":53990,"text":"is that the Internet is a private place; it's not."},{"time":56995,"text":"And with every click of the mouse and every touch of the screen,"},{"time":60080,"text":"we are like Hansel and Gretel"},{"time":62430,"text":"leaving breadcrumbs of our personal information"},{"time":65000,"text":"everywhere we travel through the digital woods."},{"time":67442,"text":"We are leaving our birthdays, our places of residence,"},{"time":72292,"text":"our interests and preferences,"},{"time":74654,"text":"our relationships,"},{"time":76743,"text":"our financial histories, and on and on it goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80504,"text":"Now don't get me wrong,"},{"time":82500,"text":"I'm not for one minute suggesting that sharing data is a bad thing."},{"time":85987,"text":"In fact, when I know the data that's being shared"},{"time":88365,"text":"and I'm asked explicitly for my consent,"},{"time":91125,"text":"I want some sites to understand my habits."},{"time":93542,"text":"It helps them suggest books for me to read"},{"time":95940,"text":"or movies for my family to watch"},{"time":98275,"text":"or friends for us to connect with."},{"time":100731,"text":"But when I don't know and when I haven't been asked,"},{"time":103812,"text":"that's when the problem arises."},{"time":106408,"text":"It's a phenomenon on the Internet today"},{"time":108125,"text":"called behavioral tracking,"},{"time":109875,"text":"and it is very big business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111542,"text":"In fact, there's an entire industry formed"},{"time":114000,"text":"around following us through the digital woods"},{"time":116337,"text":"and compiling a profile on each of us."},{"time":118681,"text":"And when all of that data is held,"},{"time":120596,"text":"they can do almost whatever they want with it."},{"time":124048,"text":"This is an area today that has very few regulations"},{"time":127417,"text":"and even fewer rules."},{"time":129167,"text":"Except for some of the recent announcements here in the United States and in Europe,"},{"time":132750,"text":"it's an area of consumer protection that's almost entirely naked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":136875,"text":"So let me expose this lurking industry a little bit further."},{"time":140279,"text":"The visualization you see forming behind me is called Collusion"},{"time":143985,"text":"and it's an experimental browser add-on"},{"time":147458,"text":"that you can install in your Firefox browser"},{"time":149625,"text":"that helps you see where your Web data is going and who's tracking you."},{"time":154321,"text":"The red dots you see up there"},{"time":156917,"text":"are sites that are behavioral tracking"},{"time":158833,"text":"that I have not navigated to, but are following me."},{"time":162042,"text":"The blue dots are the sites that I've actually navigated directly to."},{"time":165190,"text":"And the gray dots are sites that are also tracking me,"},{"time":168556,"text":"but I have no idea who they are."},{"time":170656,"text":"All of them are connected, as you can see,"},{"time":172750,"text":"to form a picture of me on the Web."},{"time":175000,"text":"And this is my profile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176542,"text":"So let me go from an example to something very specific and personal."},{"time":179952,"text":"I installed Collusion in my own laptop two weeks ago"},{"time":183375,"text":"and I let it follow me around for what was a pretty typical day."},{"time":186385,"text":"Now like most of you,"},{"time":188683,"text":"I actually start my day going online and checking email."},{"time":192304,"text":"I then go to a news site, look for some headlines."},{"time":195143,"text":"And in this particular case I happened to like one of them"},{"time":198667,"text":"on the merits of music literacy in schools"},{"time":202083,"text":"and I shared it over a social network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204333,"text":"Our daughter then joined us at the breakfast table,"},{"time":207000,"text":"and I asked her, \"Is there an emphasis on music literacy in your school?\""},{"time":211250,"text":"And she, of course, naturally as a nine-year-old,"},{"time":213250,"text":"looked at me and said quizzically, \"What's literacy?\""},{"time":215369,"text":"So I sent her online, of course, to look it up."},{"time":219125,"text":"Now let me stop here."},{"time":221250,"text":"We are not even two bites into breakfast"},{"time":224030,"text":"and there are already nearly 25 sites that are tracking me."},{"time":228346,"text":"I have navigated to a total of four."}]},{"cues":[{"time":231604,"text":"So let me fast-forward through the rest of my day."},{"time":234910,"text":"I go to work, I check email,"},{"time":237191,"text":"I log onto a few more social sites, I blog,"},{"time":239881,"text":"I check more news reports, I share some of those news reports,"},{"time":243375,"text":"I go look at some videos,"},{"time":245437,"text":"pretty typical day -- in this case, actually fairly pedantic --"},{"time":250000,"text":"and at the end of the day, as my day winds down,"},{"time":253042,"text":"look at my profile."},{"time":256083,"text":"The red dots have exploded."},{"time":258173,"text":"The gray dots have grown exponentially."},{"time":260779,"text":"All in all, there's over 150 sites"},{"time":263319,"text":"that are now tracking my personal information,"},{"time":266250,"text":"most all of them without my consent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":269092,"text":"I look at this picture and it freaks me out."},{"time":272339,"text":"This is nothing. I am being stalked across the Web."},{"time":276821,"text":"And why is this happening?"},{"time":279138,"text":"Pretty simple -- it's huge business."},{"time":281508,"text":"The revenue of the top handful of companies in this space"},{"time":284083,"text":"is over 39 billion dollars today."},{"time":286458,"text":"And as adults, we're certainly not alone."},{"time":289381,"text":"At the same time I installed my own Collusion profile,"},{"time":292375,"text":"I installed one for my daughter."},{"time":295708,"text":"And on one single Saturday morning, over two hours on the Internet,"},{"time":299083,"text":"here's her Collusion profile."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302225,"text":"This is a nine-year-old girl"},{"time":305120,"text":"navigating to principally children's sites."},{"time":308945,"text":"I move from this, from freaked out to enraged."},{"time":312417,"text":"This is no longer me being a tech pioneer or a privacy advocate;"},{"time":317127,"text":"this is me being a parent."},{"time":318727,"text":"Imagine in the physical world"},{"time":320292,"text":"if somebody followed our children around with a camera and a notebook"},{"time":323579,"text":"and recorded their every movement."},{"time":325605,"text":"I can tell you, there isn't a person in this room that would sit idly by."},{"time":329125,"text":"We'd take action. It may not be good action, but we would take action."},{"time":332550,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":333896,"text":"We can't sit idly by here either."},{"time":335961,"text":"This is happening today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338019,"text":"Privacy is not an option,"},{"time":340221,"text":"and it shouldn't be the price we accept"},{"time":342062,"text":"for just getting on the Internet."},{"time":343768,"text":"Our voices matter and our actions matter even more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347385,"text":"Today we've launched Collusion."},{"time":350458,"text":"You can download it, install it in Firefox,"},{"time":352625,"text":"to see who is tracking you across the Web"},{"time":355167,"text":"and following you through the digital woods."},{"time":357548,"text":"Going forward, all of our voices need to be heard."},{"time":360610,"text":"Because what we don't know can actually hurt us."},{"time":363750,"text":"Because the memory of the Internet is forever."},{"time":366375,"text":"We are being watched."},{"time":368054,"text":"It's now time for us to watch the watchers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":370769,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371866,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}